---
description: TypeScript strictness & lint hygiene.
globs:
  - tsconfig.json
  - src/**/*.{ts,tsx}
alwaysApply: true
---

Rules:
- TS strict mode on; no implicit any, noUnusedLocals/Parameters=true.
- ESLint: no-floating-promises, explicit return types on exported functions, prefer readonly where possible.
- Add zod or similar for runtime validation on external inputs (webhooks, query params).